{"tid":1930321,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"梁定邦冀四月公布監警會全面調查報告","createTime":"2020-03-17T12:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T17:16:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4087367e4768e423f24cb5706bc6224310bb43","tid":1930321,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】監警會主席梁定邦指，早前有挑戰監警會權力的司法覆核案將於下周二開審，會視乎裁決及諮詢法律意見，決定是否公開首階段報告；他又指希望能在4月公布涵蓋831等投訴的全面報告。<br />\n<br />\n警方指截至本月6日，共接獲1678宗與反修例事件有關的投訴，涉及逾5100名投訴人，當中569宗屬須匯報投訴，最多的指控是行為不當，有285宗；其次則為疏忽職守及濫用職權等，當中139宗完成調查，並交報告給監警會。"},{"pid":"01c83f5ea2da0e8aabef776076d034eb8f430a2f","tid":1930321,"uid":10200,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:52:45.000Z","msg":"我睇美國國務院果份唔好？"},{"pid":"469af7f20f252ca6c8a662262fa4e0c3ecd9e296","tid":1930321,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"屌你啦"},{"pid":"276209b0da626fa4c458bed8a904b4d09ea064fa","tid":1930321,"uid":260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:04:44.000Z","msg":"張建宗：不要糾纏721應「向前看」　你地重記得，我點改寫歷史啊!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1930330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1930330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1557175cb72ad2404511baf6a96f1ba7b778dbdd","tid":1930321,"uid":251732,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:07:57.000Z","msg":"跟住再借瘟疫仲未完結為由而再推遲， 甚至不了了之唔公佈"},{"pid":"c6bdaed4b0176081d87c7341fb875efe01ea9f25","tid":1930321,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2047定2048年4月？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c1606795072b1cb07931723e1c4a76a2ebfeb4ba","tid":1930321,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01c83f5ea2da0e8aabef776076d034eb8f4